DESCRIPTION:Join us on Tuesday\, June 2\, from 4 - 8 PM at Whispering Vine Fourth St. for a Flights & Flatbread tasting featuring Silver Oak and Twomey with special guest Melissa DiMaio\, Field Sales Manager.\nTasting Fee: $45 per person Includes the flight and one steak\, potato\, caramelized onion\, and blue cheese flatbread. Limited to 50 guests.\nReserve your Spot: https://www.exploretock.com/whisperingvine4thstreet/experience/540467/flights-flatbread-tasting-silver-oak\nFeatured Wines:\n- Silver Oak Napa Valley Cabernet Sauvignon 2019 – Winery $165\n- Silver Oak Alexander Valley Cabernet Sauvignon 2020 – Winery $100\n- Twomey Sauvignon Blanc 2023 – Winery $36\n- Twomey Russian River Pinot Noir 2022 – Winery $62\nFlight and flatbread included.
LOCATION:4201 W Fourth St Reno\, NV 89523
SUMMARY:Flights & Flatbread with Silver Oak
